briefdescription.para: Pointer to the reference count structure.
Construct. Allocate the reference count structure and set an initial self weak reference.
Destruct. Mark as expired and also delete the reference count structure if no outside weak references exist.

detaileddescription.para: Increment reference count. Can also be called outside of a SharedPtr for traditional reference counting. MANUAL_BIND
Decrement reference count and delete self if no more references. Can also be called outside of a SharedPtr for traditional reference counting. MANUAL_BIND

briefdescription.para: Return pointer to the reference count structure.
Base class for intrusively reference-counted objects. These are noncopyable and non-assignable.
